snippet: As touchdown celebrations have continued to evolve, many football players now engage in a not-so-new midair celebration move that so far has no name.
abstract: Touchdown celebrations have been subject to countless fads and elaborate variations, the latest of which is the midair celebration that so far has no name.
lead_paragraph: As touchdown celebrations have continued to evolve, many football players now engage in a not-so-new midair celebration move that so far has no name.

headline.seo: N.F.L.’s Latest End-Zone Dance Lacks a Name
headline.print_headline: The Run and Bump: Latest Heir To Spiked Ball Lacks a Name
